}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "8WRGAC05.1A1G" and "WRGAC05" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :The same text is found on the [[D-Link DIR-850L rev A1]]'s board in its FCC photos. :*The 5GHz radio is shown with two '''Skyworks''' SKY85703-11 FEMs. :*The Flash appears to be 16 MB (MX25L128<....>)..
The FCC sample label shows the default SSID patterns as '''dlink-XXXX''' and '''dlink-XXXX-5 GHz'''.
The power adapter shown in the FCC external photos is a '''Global Yeou Diann Electric Industrial Co., Ltd.''' AMS3-1202000FU (100-240VAC ~ 50/60 Hz, 0.8A / 65VA -> 12VDC, 2.0A).
